{"tid":2497213,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 澳洲冠軍和牛M9 Picanha","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T11:14:32.000Z","uid":260581,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"31677bf52945cccaa8836b6b38e6c77a61d807d2","tid":2497213,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日靚宵夜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n上面呢個係我第一個係連登既牛扒po<br />\n記得一年前，我一開始只係係costco買扒煎，然後就去到買唔同cutting, 去到後面自己dry aged<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇大家既支持同鼓勵，我都唔會有咁大信心整咁多野，多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我最近買左舊Stone Axe M9 Picanha, <br />\nStone Axe係2020澳洲和牛比賽既總冠軍，所以我都好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXc2suVhjAbqmshmAb3jqWfzv6zwp5zkLyga7xQ1qh1oF?filename=xCuR3oq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCuR3oq.png&h=0d8d9891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我買既時候只有15舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢舊嘢重接近2kg，價錢比我之前買過既picanha貴少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRko5yeHRzScNdNLNyX4SApzU86mBrhein7MGR1hEpRY7?filename=EskUZzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEskUZzT.jpg&h=dd642698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPx1cuPyScGCUVt36RkhKQJXM2PSBung3ZRvhNZZMYzkM?filename=Hjhgtte.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjhgtte.jpg&h=8ea561ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP4YyNScfWjervVm48AKe7sVXCkipWgxXp8cXVY29gGHF?filename=kFxTvGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFxTvGA.jpg&h=c5814ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我分左大概6塊扒，然後又係有d細舊留黎諗住過幾日打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXW9FEMnk9x5Aytf8jVaKzGmkB7PKW1Bc7qjrxR15zoMU?filename=xKPFVt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKPFVt7.jpg&h=420780b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZVqGHRnMmi9Sp4wfYmHsQ6sViD1Nq3o9joaEtMfx44ak?filename=WtGMQ2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtGMQ2u.jpg&h=86b353d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZVqGHRnMmi9Sp4wfYmHsQ6sViD1Nq3o9joaEtMfx44ak?filename=MBdWtPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBdWtPa.jpg&h=954c4cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdpexDjBxEbkSxbsbUJk2B65RMWEoZMuT13QdKGH8LMkf?filename=14Rw19c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14Rw19c.jpg&h=f8392d97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeiWzEeJqgFBBCqVfDX6HLbDC4fnJRmMEszNeA9wEqq54?filename=2RxsAue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RxsAue.jpg&h=601131d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbvA5SNsJ99EnNRNku22xAb8An9qJQgLhvqpPMMbX1gDw?filename=KKRQyfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKRQyfV.jpg&h=de673c86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTs1YGbiM1qK5usPCYaXzKW6oHossqndTQa9aQ4qX8BMY?filename=fwovyfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwovyfX.jpg&h=0991df5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYgBCzZydnQoEVcwa5Abk2D8YidfcT5C3DX3GBQoeWFpu?filename=xDf9OPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDf9OPj.jpg&h=393cffcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我拎去reverse sear, 冇salt brine<br />\n塊野都好juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3tm6XibLMgEynXT9cvfHSY9jQCaDZUwbGPrfqwTz2Uq?filename=wDAUZWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDAUZWT.jpg&h=6c6e1b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUCjGzrQh4DLVHomC5yawrKxaca8qn9V8THeGAwcnPRio?filename=A1jOjWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1jOjWV.jpg&h=978dbdf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVjjyA4yJKiLk1kwzkGCda5tVLrVAg5VHGwvJCMpfFq7J?filename=KVNHpoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVNHpoC.jpg&h=950802cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVy43kVZnEaosjKoakRf72UvKUJrRkJUNEAwihUN4XbqA?filename=FTvFa3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTvFa3D.jpg&h=5432fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVGBcAXbs5dEdztsLK3r8Bhfk7PC7ckrUUB4TBfCqkVEx?filename=BF33TgZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBF33TgZ.jpg&h=7625254a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcEZxZnx1SGCXPop7cecnj2