assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCuR3oq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCuR3oq.png&h=0d8d9891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我買既時候只有15舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢舊嘢重接近2kg，價錢比我之前買過既picanha貴少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EskUZzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEskUZzT.jpg&h=dd642698&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hjhgtte.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjhgtte.jpg&h=8ea561ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFxTvGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFxTvGA.jpg&h=c5814ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我分左大概6塊扒，然後又係有d細舊留黎諗住過幾日打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKPFVt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKPFVt7.jpg&h=420780b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtGMQ2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtGMQ2u.jpg&h=86b353d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBdWtPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBdWtPa.jpg&h=954c4cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14Rw19c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14Rw19c.jpg&h=f83